OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOver 2,000 fines for       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fparents due to pupil       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fabsences                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, More than 2,000 fines were issued to   
OL,6, parents in Wales last year because     
OL,7, their children were missing school.    
OL,9,FSome councils used hundreds of fixed   
OL,10,Fpenalty notices (FPNs) to tackle       
OL,11,Fabsences, although others did not issue
OL,12,Fany, figures showed.                   
OL,14,FOne mum, Ebony Mullen from Pontypridd, 
OL,15,FRhondda Cynon Taf, said schools should 
OL,16,Fbe flexible as some parents could only 
OL,17,Fafford holidays during term time.      
OL,19,FWelsh government guidance said fines   
OL,20,Fshould only be used as a last resort.  
